zey hobn undz farnikhtikt di papirn, zey hobn undz keyn mol nisht gegebn tsu visn afile az undz ho'mir papirn, az s'iz gekumen.

398
00:23:11,153 --> 00:23:12,784
s'geven dort a froy,

399
00:23:12,975 --> 00:23:17,908
a shvaybishe, dos hot geheysn azoy halb daytshe froy, zi iz

400
00:23:17,908 --> 00:23:23,451
UNK zi hot undz geflegt zogn, "vayter iz aykh ongekumen papirn, vayter iz avekgeganen in RUBBISH."

401
00:23:23,451 --> 00:23:26,215
zey hobn undz nisht gegebn tsu visn az undz ho'mir papirn.

402
00:23:26,526 --> 00:23:28,747
vi veystu yetst host yetst host,

403
00:23:29,310 --> 00:23:33,016
neyn demolts ho'mir undz gevust, vayl di froy iz gekumen un zi hot undz alts gezogt.

404
00:23:29,395 --> 00:23:30,401
zey hot ge-

405
00:23:33,394 --> 00:23:35,666
undz hot men nisht tsu visn getun funem

406
00:23:35,892 --> 00:23:46,773
funem fun zey az undz ho'mir papirn, ober di froy hot undz alts gezogt, s'iz vayter gekumen, zi hot alts bakumen a matone fun undz, un zi hot undz ales tsu visn getun, andersh het mir undz nisht gevust az, der

407
00:23:46,773 --> 00:23:49,926
der tate hot der nokh dem geshribn alts, mir ho'mir geshikt.

408
00:23:48,750 --> 00:23:50,181
s'iz ge- zey hobn,

409
00:23:50,181 --> 00:23:55,646
s'geven azoy vayl du host geven yidn? ober bloyz rusishe kon nisht aroysgeyn?

410
00:23:57,306 --> 00:24:02,919
UNK demolts in yene tsayt, koydem hobn zey undz nisht gelozt vayl zey hobn gehaltn mayn tate far a shpyon.

411
00:24:03,938 --> 00:24:06,373
zey hobn im nisht genumen az er iz antlofn.

412
00:24:06,373 --> 00:24:10,344
zey hobn genumen di mentshn far shpyonen, az far dem zenen zey antlofn.

413
00:24:11,768 --> 00:24:15,626
un di tsveyte mol hobn zey nisht aroysgelozt demolts keyn mentshn

414
00:24:17,067 --> 00:24:18,355
durkh der grenets.

415
00:24:18,355 --> 00:24:19,659
s'iz geven

416
00:24:20,172 --> 00:24:25,380
ergets ergets zeyer zeltns vos a mentsh az zey hobn aroysgelozt,

417
00:24:25,487 --> 00:24:28,799
ikh vel zogn ven m'hot aroysgelozt shoyn, m'hot ongehoybn tsu lozn,

418
00:24:28,799 --> 00:24:32,821
mayn khaverte iz avekgeganen in fir un zekhtsiker yor

419
00:24:35,241 --> 00:24:38,627
keyn Erets, demolts hot men ongehoybn zikh tsu rirn.

420
00:24:38,785 --> 00:24:39,938
ober azoy neyn.

421
00:24:39,938 --> 00:24:41,529
vu m'hot gelozt,

422
00:24:41,856 --> 00:24:45,748
hot men gelozt of Ungarn, oyf Ungarn,

423
00:24:46,007 --> 00:24:49,309
oykhet nor az m'hot mishpokhe,

424
00:24:49,416 --> 00:24:52,245
m'hot ongehoybn nokh tsu lozn, ober nisht keyn yidn.

425
00:24:52,875 --> 00:24:55,586
m'hot nisht gelozt keyn yidn aroys in ergets nisht.

426
00:24:54,546 --> 00:24:58,691
zey hobn gemakht di zeyer hart far yidn ober far ale?

427
00:24:57,938 --> 00:25:07,343
far ale ober far di yidn nokh beser, vayl di yidn merstes teyl yidn iz geven nor Amerike un un oyf vu zey hobn dort gehat di fraynt,

428
00:25:07,343 --> 00:25:10,217
un oyf Erets,

429
00:25:10,611 --> 00:25:12,866
un mit Erets hobn zey

430
00:25:12,990 --> 00:25:15,717
zenen zey geven di greste sonim far undz.

431
00:25:15,741 --> 00:25:19,602
un du host geveyst vos iz gemakht in andere orter in di velt?

432
00:25:19,082 --> 00:25:21,753
yo BETACH, undz ho'mir oysgehert radyo.

433
00:25:19,602 --> 00:25:20,713
du host gehert?

434
00:25:21,753 --> 00:25:22,906
bishtike.

435
00:25:23,267 --> 00:25:26,400
undz ho'mir oysgehert, s'geven a radyo fun Amerike,

436
00:25:26,727 --> 00:25:32,154
vos er hot ibergegebn aldings vos s'tut zikh.

437
00:25:32,667 --> 00:25:39,700
un m- ikh hob mikh geshribn keyn Erets mit khaveyrim, ikh hob mikh geshribn ale yorn keyn Amerike mit khavertes,

438
00:25:39,700 --> 00:25:42,931
vos biz haynt, velkhe zenen nisht geshtorbn,

439
00:25:42,931 --> 00:25:45,452
ze'mir undz in in a tifn kontakt.

440
00:25:46,234 --> 00:25:48,894
un ven hostu aroysgeganen Rus?

441
00:25:50,892 --> 00:25:54,109
mayn tate iz geshtorbn in tsvey un zekhtsiker yor,

442
00:25:54,942 --> 00:25:56,674
er hot bakumen a,

443
00:25:57,895 --> 00:26:02,496
zog mir nisht, keyn atak fun kop dos blut, ikh veys vi azoy heyst es, vi azoy,

444
00:26:02,535 --> 00:26:05,549
er iz geshtorbn fraytik oyf der nakht baym tish.

445
00:26:06,923 --> 00:26:09,262
ober er iz geshtorbn

446
00:26:09,420 --> 00:26:15,483
danken far undz, er hot shtark a sakh ibergelebt far undz, vayl er hot gevust az undz ze'mir zeyer,

447
00:26:15,483 --> 00:26:19,472
vayl der tsvishn iz nokh mayn man geven opgeshpart oykhet.

448
00:26:19,495 --> 00:26:21,969
er iz nokh a yor gezesn in tfise oykhet,

449
00:26:22,448 --> 00:26:25,794
vos ven nisht mayn tate zitst er gevezn

450
00:26:25,794 --> 00:26:27,690
khotshik zeks akht yor.

451
00:26:28,810 --> 00:26:34,254
ober der mayn tate ven der advokat iz gekumen fun Moskve voynen keyn Tetsh,

452
00:26:34,564 --> 00:26:36,414
un mayn tate iz gevezn

453
00:26:36,893 --> 00:26:40,920
zeyer sh- raykh demolts, er hot gehat a sakh gelt, un der

454
00:26:41,010 --> 00:26:47,129
der advokat iz gekumen mit eyn fus un mit dray kinder un azoy orem az got zol ophitn,

455
00:26:47,541 --> 00:26:51,062
un mayn tate hot im aroyfgeshtelt oyf di fis,

456
00:26:51,321 --> 00:26:55,871
un ven er iz antlofn hot er im, er iz gevezn zayn advokat,

457
00:26:55,995 --> 00:27:00,413
un ven mayn man hot men opgeshpart, hot er gezogt, hitst iz gekumen di tsayt

458
00:27:00,413 --> 00:27:04,595
ven ikh vel dir revanshirn a bisele nor vos dayn tate hot mikh getun.

459
00:27:04,787 --> 00:27:09,877
un er iz geven eyner fun di beste advokatn hot zikh gerekhnt

460
00:27:09,968 --> 00:27:11,565
in Rusnland.

461
00:27:11,655 --> 00:27:15,378
ober iz gekumen keyn Karpatn voynen, tsun undz,

462
00:27:15,891 --> 00:27:16,661
un

463
00:27:16,684 --> 00:27:22,230
er hot mir geholfn mayn man aroystsune- er iz gekumen tsu forn, er hot shoyn nisht gevoynt in undzer shtot,

464
00:27:22,236 --> 00:27:24,739
er iz gekumen tsu forn tsu mir,

465
00:27:24,739 --> 00:27:28,170
un er hot nisht genumen bayn undz keyn eyn tsent nisht.

466
00:27:28,159 --> 00:27:29,570
vos iz geven dem nomen?

467
00:27:29,577 --> 00:27:31,781
Doktor Vaser, hot er geheysn.

468
00:27:32,867 --> 00:27:36,776
un vi hostu aroysgekumen fun Rusland?

469
00:27:36,782 --> 00:27:39,121
fun Rusnalnd iz mayn mume

470
00:27:39,786 --> 00:27:45,129
mit der mishpokhe hot bakumen fun a bruder vos er iz aroysgeforn befor,

471
00:27:46,350 --> 00:27:52,067
zi hot gehat dort a bruder shoyn draysik yor, un nokh dem hot zi gehat nokh eynem vos er iz shpeter aroysgeforn,

472
00:27:52,067 --> 00:27:54,478
un der bruder vos er iz

473
00:27:54,838 --> 00:27:57,754
shpeter aroysgeforn hot ir geshikt dokumentn.

474
00:27:57,754 --> 00:27:58,781
papirn.

475
00:27:59,850 --> 00:28:03,154
un mayn mume hot nokh gehat dray khadoshim tsu f-

476
00:28:03,154 --> 00:28:06,577
tsu pakn zikh, ober ales iz geven ongeport

477
00:28:06,617 --> 00:28:10,374
mit di familye aroystsugeyn, zey hobn gevoynt di drite shtub fun undz,

478
00:28:11,207 --> 00:28:17,124
un demolts iz gegan mayn mume, s'iz demolts hot oysgekrakht di zeks-togedike milkhome,

479
00:28:17,451 --> 00:28:20,111
un m'hot farshpart ale grenetsn,

480
00:28:20,168 --> 00:28:24,206
un m'hot di diplomatishe batsiung opgehakt,

481
00:28:24,206 --> 00:28:29,713
mayn mume iz geven di letste vos zi iz durkhgegan der grenets mit di familye bayn undz,

482
00:28:29,888 --> 00:28:34,523
ven m'hot opgeshpart di diplomatishe batsiung.

483
00:28:34,815 --> 00:28:37,239
un mayn mume hot dort gevoynt a por yor,

484
00:28:37,650 --> 00:28:39,331
undz ho'mir zikh geshribn,

485
00:28:39,979 --> 00:28:43,618
un zi hot gevust shoyn az nisht zi demolts keyner nisht.

486
00:28:43,860 --> 00:28:45,350
hot undz geshikt

487
00:28:45,350 --> 00:28:49,068
papirn, zi hot undz geshikt eyn mol, zi hot geshikt tsvey mol,

488
00:28:49,243 --> 00:28:51,481
ober m'hot zey ongenumen.

489
00:28:52,197 --> 00:28:53,602
in a zumer,

490
00:28:53,602 --> 00:28:56,206
undz ze'mir geven shoyn zeyer gut aranzhirt,

491
00:28:56,280 --> 00:28:58,366
vayl mayn tate hot mikh

492
00:28:58,963 --> 00:29:02,011
zeyer aranzhirt, nisht fun undzer arbet,

493
00:29:02,828 --> 00:29:07,479
un ikh hob shoyn gekont mir erloybn tsu batsoln az undz zo'mir konen

494
00:29:07,587 --> 00:29:09,268
fun dort aroys shpringen.

495
00:29:09,493 --> 00:29:10,904
un demolts

496
00:29:11,552 --> 00:29:14,367
iz gekumen eyner vos er iz gevezn

497
00:29:14,367 --> 00:29:17,824
zeyer a raykher mentsh fun an andere shtot,

498
00:29:18,555 --> 00:29:20,439
un er hot mir ongetrogn

499
00:29:21,222 --> 00:29:22,701
az s'iz do,

500
00:29:23,128 --> 00:29:27,408
di groyse kep zenen ale avekgeforn oyf HOLIDAY, oyf

501
00:29:27,718 --> 00:29:28,939
CHOFESH.

502
00:29:28,939 --> 00:29:30,362
s'iz geven zumer.

503
00:29:31,414 --> 00:29:36,166
un er iz geven zeyer a toyglekher bokher, zogt er, ikh vel mikh opshmuesn mit di kleyne,

504
00:29:36,257 --> 00:29:39,305
efshere m'vet zikh, ve'mir konen aroysshpringen,

505
00:29:39,328 --> 00:29:43,544
khotshik tsvey dray familyes, eyn familye iz nisht geven interesant vays s'iz nisht geven genug

506
00:29:43,544 --> 00:29:44,942
zey tsu batsoln.

507
00:29:45,454 --> 00:29:47,692
un er hot mir ongetrogn dos.

508
00:29:48,171 --> 00:29:58,644
un undz ho'mir batsolt, er iz ge- vifl er hot gezogt, azoy fil hob ikh gegebn un nokh a mishpokhe un er, un undz ho'mir zikh in tsvey khadoshim opgepakt un avekgegan.

509
00:29:59,038 --> 00:30:00,314
m'darf,

510
00:30:00,186 --> 00:30:00,993
toyshn.

511
00:30:01,182 --> 00:30:01,702
yo.

